23 SECTION 1-1001.
24 Reincorporation.
25 The City of Cleveland, in White County, and the inhabitants thereof, are reincorporated by
26 the enactment of this charter and are hereby constituted and declared a body politic and
27 corporate under the name and style of the City of Cleveland, Georgia, and by that name shall
28 have perpetual succession.
29 SECTION 1-1002.
30 Corporate boundaries.
