34 a written description, or any combination thereof, to be retained permanently in the office of
35 the city clerk and to be designated, as the case may be: "Official Map (or Description) of the
36 corporate limits of the City of Cleveland, Georgia, in White County, Georgia." Photographic,
37 typed, or other copies of such map or description certified by the city clerk shall be admitted
